{"tid":1840104,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"如果要你砌歷史最強陣容會點砌？","createTime":"2020-01-24T17:01:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-26T15:37:02.000Z","uid":160589,"like":1,"dislike":33,"uniUserReply":45,"replies":[{"pid":"ee8bde7aa55787639ada9cffc663c12c7de3375b","tid":1840104,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:01:35.000Z","msg":"牙朗 大哨 美斯<br />\n      老馬   韋拉 施丹 <br />\n馬甸尼 碧根鮑華 vvd 卡富<br />\n<br />\n前鋒其實牙朗可以代替埋大哨 但諗唔到左邊放邊個好<br />\n比利覺得佢身型麻麻 技術無美斯咁好 加上年代太遠 個時既足球有種未成熟既感覺 副選心水有普斯卡斯 <br />\n<br />\n中場最難諗係防中 無邊個係勁到非選不可 應該好多人覺得馬基里利可以 因為進攻夠人 放個防守勁既就得 但如果係咁簡迪仲勁 但無制空力 中場其他人選忍痛放棄有迪史提芬奴 小白 告老夫 柏天尼<br />\n<br />\n後衛最易諗 馬同碧唔洗講啦 vvd論條件我覺得真係完美  右閘我一定簡攻守都有 所以艾維斯個類放棄 得返辛尼迪同卡富 卡富能力稍勝"},{"pid":"f0ba860a127d35821e042c49a2c2662f40e7a1a3","tid":1840104,"uid":16659,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"gk都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"20a74e70b0944baabda60930da0c058751ac1bae","tid":1840104,"uid":158933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"比利啦"},{"pid":"79bbc13bfc829bb9841edba80ec3884ad7a5c7e8","tid":1840104,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"quote":{"pid":"f0ba860a127d35821e042c49a2c2662f40e7a1a3","tid":1840104,"uid":16659,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:08:32.000Z","msg":"gk都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:09:48.000Z","msg":"Sir yashin<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個無爭議 神人黎"},{"pid":"da8074eb12185bc2f958d26cd4b7c05eb4766d42","tid":1840104,"uid":160589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"20a74e70b0944baabda60930da0c058751ac1bae","tid":1840104,"uid":158933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:08:57.000Z","msg":"比利啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T17:10:52.000Z","msg":"邊個位先放"},{"pid":"738596055d8b8